---
import Layout from '../layouts/PageWithTitle.astro';
import { GITHUB_REPO } from '../consts';
import augustPhoto from '../assets/august_photo.jpeg';
---

<Layout
	title="The Company"
>
	<p>
		Fieldwork was inspired by our shared frustrations with developing firmware. We felt that coding agents 
		do not perform as well at low-level embedded work as they do at the more common application/web/scripting work.
	</p>
	<p>
		The reason for this is simple - these tasks are under-represented in training data. Our aim here is to fill in that gap.
	</p>
	<div class="section-title">
		<h1>The People</h1>
		<hr />
	</div>
	<div class="people-grid">
		<article class="person-card">
			<figure>
				<div class="headshot-placeholder" role="img" aria-label="Headshot placeholder for Person 1"></div>
				<figcaption>
					Tim Krasnoperov, Co-Founder / CEO
					<a
						class="linkedin-link"
						href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/placeholder-tim-krasnoperov/"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						aria-label="Tim Krasnoperov LinkedIn profile"
					>
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
							<path
								d="M19 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2zM8.09 18H5.56V9.81h2.53zM6.83 8.68a1.47 1.47 0 1 1 0-2.94 1.47 1.47 0 0 1 0 2.94zM18.44 18h-2.53v-3.98c0-.95-.02-2.18-1.33-2.18-1.33 0-1.53 1.04-1.53 2.11V18h-2.53V9.81h2.43v1.12h.03c.34-.64 1.17-1.32 2.41-1.32 2.57 0 3.05 1.69 3.05 3.89z"
							/>
						</svg>
					</a>
				</figcaption>
			</figure>
			<p>TK is an Senior AI engineer at LinkedIn and got his CS bachelors from Caltech. 
			In his free time, he wrote the algorithms behind axtheory.com. TK is leading the project by designing 
			the eval/training pipelines and the verifier libraries, creating tasks, and analyzing what the models 
			are getting wrong. </p>
		</article>
		<article class="person-card">
			<figure>
				<img class="headshot" src={augustPhoto.src} alt="August O'Beirne headshot" loading="lazy" />
				<figcaption>
					August O'Beirne, Co-Founder
					<a
						class="linkedin-link"
						href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/august-obeirne/"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						aria-label="August O'Beirne LinkedIn profile"
					>
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
							<path
								d="M19 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2zM8.09 18H5.56V9.81h2.53zM6.83 8.68a1.47 1.47 0 1 1 0-2.94 1.47 1.47 0 0 1 0 2.94zM18.44 18h-2.53v-3.98c0-.95-.02-2.18-1.33-2.18-1.33 0-1.53 1.04-1.53 2.11V18h-2.53V9.81h2.43v1.12h.03c.34-.64 1.17-1.32 2.41-1.32 2.57 0 3.05 1.69 3.05 3.89z"
							/>
						</svg>
					</a>
				</figcaption>
			</figure>
			<p>August is a civil engineer, experienced project manager, and CS minor from UW Seattle - bringing expertise from exposure to 
			FAA electronics engineering and personal IoT and microcontroller projects. 
			August manages the taxonomy, runs the observability/monitoring platforms, 
			writes tasks, performs PM and admin duties, and handles all front-end work across the company. </p>
		</article>
		<article class="person-card">
			<figure>
				<div class="headshot-placeholder" role="img" aria-label="Headshot placeholder for Person 3"></div>
				<figcaption>
					Conlon Meek, Co-Founder
					<a
						class="linkedin-link"
						href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/placeholder-conlon-meek/"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						aria-label="Conlon Meek LinkedIn profile"
					>
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
							<path
								d="M19 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2zM8.09 18H5.56V9.81h2.53zM6.83 8.68a1.47 1.47 0 1 1 0-2.94 1.47 1.47 0 0 1 0 2.94zM18.44 18h-2.53v-3.98c0-.95-.02-2.18-1.33-2.18-1.33 0-1.53 1.04-1.53 2.11V18h-2.53V9.81h2.43v1.12h.03c.34-.64 1.17-1.32 2.41-1.32 2.57 0 3.05 1.69 3.05 3.89z"
							/>
						</svg>
					</a>
				</figcaption>
			</figure>
			<p>Conlon is an experienced electrical and hardware engineer. 
			He is responsible for designing our custom circuits, sourcing components, and 
			verifying the electricity works as expected. In his free time, 
			Conlon runs axtheory.com. He comes from UC Berkley and currently works at a solar engineering company in NYC. </p>
		</article>
		<article class="person-card">
			<figure>
				<div class="headshot-placeholder" role="img" aria-label="Headshot placeholder for Person 4"></div>
				<figcaption>
					Matt McColgan, Co-Founder
					<a
						class="linkedin-link"
						href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/placeholder-matt-mccoolgan/"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						aria-label="Matt McCoolgan LinkedIn profile"
					>
						<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
							<path
								d="M19 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2zM8.09 18H5.56V9.81h2.53zM6.83 8.68a1.47 1.47 0 1 1 0-2.94 1.47 1.47 0 0 1 0 2.94zM18.44 18h-2.53v-3.98c0-.95-.02-2.18-1.33-2.18-1.33 0-1.53 1.04-1.53 2.11V18h-2.53V9.81h2.43v1.12h.03c.34-.64 1.17-1.32 2.41-1.32 2.57 0 3.05 1.69 3.05 3.89z"
							/>
						</svg>
					</a>
				</figcaption>
			</figure>
			<p>Matt is a Physics + CS double major from UC Berkley, and has spent 6 years as a cuber-security expert 
			working at Tanium. He is our lead on the software-to-hardware interface, the deployment infrastructure, 
			virtualization, and contributes security-based tasks to our benchmark.</p>
		</article>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	:global(.prose) {
		width: 920px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2em);
	}

	:global(.prose p),
	:global(.prose li),
	:global(.prose figcaption) {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.section-title {
		margin-bottom: 1em;
		padding: 1em 0;
		text-align: center;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.section-title h1 {
		margin: 0 0 0.5em 0;
	}

	.people-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.person-card {
		padding: 1rem;
		border: 1px solid #d9d9d9;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
	}

	.person-card figure {
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
	}

	.headshot-placeholder {
		aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
		width: 100%;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #efefef, #d9d9d9);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.headshot {
		aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
		width: 100%;
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		object-fit: cover;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.person-card figcaption {
		font-weight: 600;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.person-card p {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.linkedin-link {
		display: inline-flex;
		color: #8a8f98;
	}

	.linkedin-link svg {
		width: 1.35rem;
		height: 1.35rem;
		fill: currentColor;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.people-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
